title: Maruti Suzuki's total vehicle sales rise 15.5 pc at 1,99,364 units in January
description: Maruti Suzuki India's total vehicle sales, including exports, increased 5 per cent at 1,99,364 units in January from 1,72,535 units in the same month last year, the company said in a statement on Thursday. This was the highest-ever monthly sales volume for the Gurugram-based car maker, as per the statement.
